data.description: Don't let this market stop you from owning a beautiful better-than-new home!  This house comes with an assumable VA loan @ 5.125% and early occupancy options are available to accommodate your moving timeframe. Title work is already started at Stewart Title so make your offer and prepare for your move-in today! This delightful neighborhood near the turnpike offers a sprayground and stocked pond. The Jasmine design begins with an open Entry Hall w/10' ceiling w/crown molding & 6' niche for art/furniture. Fantastic Flex Room with 10' vaulted ceiling. Bedroom hall with no view into the rooms from the Foyer for privacy. Great Room with 12' vaulted ceiling and wood look ceramic tile. Large Breakfast Nook. Kitchen with built-in appliances & spacious walk-in pantry. Master Suite includes wonderful sitting area with 2 windows, additional 3 windows for plenty of natural light, and built-in bookshelves. Master Bath with large closet, dual vanities, walk-in shower, large walk-in master closet with convenient access door to Laundry Room. Laundry Room opens to bedroom hall and has two additional storage closets. Utility room includes 48" mud bench and coat closet. Extra 648 cubic feet of storage space area in garage (81 sq. ft. floor space).  Owner upgrades include soft-close hinges and pull-down faucet sprayer in the kitchen, extra outlets in the garage, and a completely fenced-in back yard.
